<#assign product = event.product_detail.value()?eval>
<#assign cart = event.cart_data.value()?eval>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Don't forget your abandoned product!</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <img src="[Company Logo]" alt="[Company Name] Logo" width="200" height="100">
    </div>
    <h1>Don't forget your abandoned product!</h1>
    <p>Dear 
        <#if user.firstname.value()?has_content>
            ${user.firsname.value()},
        <#else>
            Valued Customer,
        </#if>
    </p>
    <p>We noticed that you left <strong>${product.name}</strong> in your cart without completing your purchase. We understand that sometimes things come up, but we don't want you to miss out on the opportunity to enjoy <strong>[Product Name]</strong>.</p>
    <p>As a valued customer of [Company Name], we're pleased to offer you an exclusive discount of <strong>[10%]</strong> off your purchase. Use the code <strong>[111111]</strong> at checkout to redeem your discount.</p>
    <div>
      <img src="${product.image_url}" alt="${product.name}" width="200" height="100">
    </div>
    <p>Here are the details of the abandoned product:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>[${product.name}]</strong></li>
      <li>Price: <strong>${event.cart_value.value()}${event.cart_currency.value()}</strong></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Simply click the button below to return to your cart and complete your purchase.</p>
    <div>
      <a href="${cart.cart_url}"><button style="background-color: #008CBA; border: none; color: white; padding: 15px 32px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; margin: 4px 2px; cursor: pointer;">Return to Cart</button></a>
    </div>
    <p>Thank you for considering [Company Name]. We appreciate your business and look forward to serving you soon.</p>
    <div>
      <img src="[Company Logo]" alt="[Company Name] Logo" width="200" height="100">
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
